chart_description: This chart displays changes in memory usage of the main cache used by Netdata's DBengine. It provides details on the amount of data evicted from cache and the addition of new data as clean and hot.

dimension_descriptions.evictions: The amount of data in bytes that has been evicted from the cache.
dimension_descriptions.new clean: The amount of clean data in bytes stored in cache.
dimension_descriptions.new hot: The amount of hot data in bytes stored in cache.
